    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small drinking glasses for cocktails, with a foot, stem, and bowl, which varies in shape and size but is often funnel-shaped.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
